Enum JobHistory.Keys

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JobHistory.Keys>
      • org.apache.hadoop.mapred.JobHistory.Keys
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<JobHistory.Keys>
    Enclosing class:
    JobHistory

    public static enum JobHistory.Keys
extends Enum<JobHistory.Keys>
    Job history files contain key="value" pairs, where keys belong to this enum. It acts as a global namespace for all keys.
